    "title": "Career Opportunity Software Engineer at Oracle India Asia Pacific Associates",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Software Engineer with drive and ambition, Oracle India Asia Pacific Associates in Howrah is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Oracle India Asia Pacific Associates:\nOracle India Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Python\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Howrah, West Bengal, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Oracle India Asia Pacific Associates!",
